content: A photo from a walk on 2025-03-29.

photos.alt: A photo of a magnolia tree with pink flowers blooming. Many of the flowers are in focus, below the tree there is a green bench, some bushes, and a few petals on the asphalt and ground. The sky is bright blue, a gradient from darker color on top, to a lighter one on the bottom. Behind the tree there are some out of focus buildings, signs, and cars.
